# TreeStump Conventions

## Stack
- Vite + React 19 + TypeScript (strict) + Tailwind CSS v4 + Zustand
- React Router v7 HashRouter for GitHub Pages compatibility

## File Organization
- `src/components/` — React components, one component per file
- `src/lib/` — Pure functions with no React dependencies (parser, layout, export)
- `src/stores/` — Zustand stores
- `src/types.ts` — Shared type definitions

## Coding Style
- Functional components with named exports as default
- Prefer `function` declarations over arrow functions for components
- Use Tailwind utility classes; avoid separate CSS files per component
- All colors, fonts, and radii come from the theme tokens in `index.css`
- State: use `useProjectStore` for global state, local `useState` for UI-only state
- Derived data (parsed tree, layout): compute via `useMemo`, never store in Zustand

## Design Tokens (from Sunday.ai)
- Background: `bg` (#ffffff)
- Text: `primary` (#1a1a1a), `secondary` (60% opacity)
- Accent: `accent` (#f7e731)
- Surfaces: `surface` (#f3f3f0), `surface-secondary` (#ecece8)
- Border: `border` (#1a1a1a at 10%)
- Border radius: 12px default, 9999px for pills
- Fonts: `--font-sans` (Geist), `--font-mono` (Geist Mono)

## Data Flow
```
bracketText → parse() → TreeNode → layoutTree() → PositionedNode[] → <TreeView /> (SVG)
```
